                        → Changelog
                    </a>
                </p>
            </section>

            <hr style="margin: 3rem 0; opacity: 0.1;" />

            <section>
                <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center;">
                    <em>QAIL is open-source and MIT-licensed. Built in Rust. Deployed on Cloudflare.
